Description: If TRUE, turn on display of NRIC field on Wound PDF report

If TRUE, NRIC field on Wound PDF report will be masked to only show last 4 char. If FALSE, NRIC field on Wound PDF report will display full NRIC or masked NRIC depending on the user's access rights when viewing / downloading the report
Bed of patient profile input will be required if TRUE
Location of patient profile input will be required if TRUE
Ward of patient profile input will be required if TRUE
